  <brief_title>CPASMA: Is There an Improvement in Asthma in Patients With Both Asthma and OSAS Treated With CPAP?</brief_title>
  <acronym>CPASMA</acronym>
  <official_title>The CPASMA Trial: Is There an Improvement in Asthma in Patients With Both Asthma and Obstructive Sleep Apnoea Syndrome (OSAS) Treated With Continuous Positive Airway Pressure (CPAP) After Six Months?</official_title>
