  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult patients (18 to 70 yrs.) with asthma who require treatment with CPAP because of
             OSAS (RDI&gt; = 20 events per hour)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  unstable or severe comorbidity,

          -  patients in treatment with drugs that interfere with the clinical course of asthma
             and/or OSAS,

          -  cognitive/psychiatric disorders that preclude patient participation/cooperation,

          -  COPD or other lung disease accompanied by chronic airflow limitation, and

          -  any clinical condition considered severe enough by the investigators to preclude all
             the diagnostic and therapeutic procedures outlined in this protocol.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
